HEADWORD: Fallfish
<hw>Fall"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A fresh-water fish of the United States (<spn>Semotilus
bullaris</spn>); -- called also <altname>silver chub</altname>, and
<altname>Shiner</altname>. The name is also applied to other allied
species.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

